/>\n<br />\n有冇諗過入得遠月都係天才"},{"pid":"bcade16024a02a8c981b80c2cac6960a851ecfc5","tid":465300,"uid":38775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"女主角田所惠世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4094428d0e37629fb54ebb67eab78c5a40b2577","tid":465300,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話主角集百家大乘一挑10仲好睇</blockquote><br />\n會唔會畫幸平輸呢？</blockquote><br />\n係都唔奇<br />\n如果而家一年級就贏埋一席咁仲使咩畫落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係輸比司或龍膽<br />\n最後比全力出擊嘅一色/大小姐尾刀打贏鬼父<br />\n尤其係繪理奈, 如果由佢親手打贏咁先會話佢有成長同走出鬼父陰影<br />\n<br />\n另外我硬係覺得龍膽學姐最後會倒戈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢一直都無特別認同鬼父<br />\n又反對踢久我一色等人出十傑<br />\n又阻止顏藝王收買評判<br />\n學園祭又顯示出佢咩都想試食唔似鬼父要有個標準答案咁<br />\n可能遲啲佢覺得玩夠, 鬼父比唔到滿足感佢時佢就倒戈去 <del>做後宮</del> 主角陣營"},{"pid":"62768d19f4d0b00493e418fd8dfdb3f7cd7a7680","tid":465300,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"田所G輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藥王贏埋跟住應該同塔打柒四席 跟住到第二日5抽2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753b2b01562b95c3367d99234280667d2d612746","tid":465300,"uid":21226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"田所好細波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8d257b6d41e1fef14a0a77c255e91b9b05d826","tid":465300,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女主角田所惠世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0957f7885ff9f2d64c6d60bff194775e06164945","tid":465300,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><bloc